        <h2 class="text-3xl font-[Georgia] text-[#3b1f0e] mb-6">Understanding Cyber Rehabilitation</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          In the ever-evolving landscape of technology, Avanzo stands at the forefront, pioneering a transformative initiative—Cyber Rehabilitation. Rooted in the belief that everyone deserves a chance at redemption and growth, Avanzo has embarked on a mission to rehabilitate individuals who have succumbed to the darker aspects of the digital world.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
          At the heart of Avanzo’s Cyber Rehabilitation is a holistic approach that addresses not only the symptoms but also the underlying causes of digital maladaptive behavior. The program encompasses psychological counseling, educational workshops, vocational training, and community support to provide a well-rounded and personalized rehabilitation experience.
        </p>
